Duri neMutswi (large food preparation mortar and pestle) mudziyo unoshandiswa kupwanya kana kuti kutswa mbeu dzinodyiwa dzakaita se[[chibage]]; nzungu; [[zviyo]]; [[mhunga]] nezvimwewo. Duri rinoshandiswa pamwe ne[[mutswi]]. 

MuZimbabwe duri rinoshandiswa pakutswa nzungu panogadzirwa dovi uye chibage panogadzirwa [[manhuchu]]. Kudzvura kunogona kushandwa nemunhu mumwe chete aine mutswi mumwe kana kuitwa nevanhu vaviri vaine [[mutswi]] miviri muduri rimwechete.
